  "title": "Generational Cycling Under Damage",
  "concept": "When harm cannot be avoided, populations persist by accelerating reproduction—more frequent generational turnover compensates for individual damage accumulation, keeping population size stable even as component lifespans shorten.",
  "interactiveId": "4b2cf2d7-44eb-4c2a-973d-b7d3e036edf9",
  "sourcePieceId": "cee5e838-4718-4847-a229-b9271b6cb7ea",
  "publishedAt": 1777212488071,
  "voiceScore": 90,
  "qualityFlag": "low",
  "content": {
    "type": "html",
    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n<title>Generational Cycling Under Damage</title>\n<style>\n  :root {\n    --bg: #faf7f1;\n    --fg: #1a1a1a;\n    --muted: #6b6b6b;\n    --line: #e5e0d6;\n    --primary: #c9a227;\n    --accent: #1a6b62;\n  }\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n  body {\n    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif;\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 20px;\n    color: var(--fg);\n    background: var(--bg);\n    line-height: 1.5;\n  }\n  h2 {\n    font-size: 1.05rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin: 0 0 4px;\n  }\n  p.subhead {\n    margin: 0 0 20px;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .control {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 14px;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n  }\n  .control label {\n    font-weight: 500;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n  .control input[type=range] {\n    flex: 1;\n    accent-color: var(--accent);\n    min-width: 120px;\n  }\n  .control output {\n    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    min-width: 4ch;\n    text-align: right;\n  }\n  .timeline {\n    margin: 24px 0;\n    padding: 16px;\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n  }\n  .timeline-title {\n    font-size: 0.8rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.04em;\n    color: var(--muted);\n  }\n  .gen-track {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 4px;\n    margin: 8px 0;\n    height: 32px;\n    align-items: center;\n  }\n  .gen-marker {\n    height: 24px;\n    background: var(--primary);\n    border-radius: 3px;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    transition: all 180ms ease-out;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  .gen-marker.damaged {\n    opacity: 0.4;\n  }\n  .metrics {\n    margin: 18px 0;\n    padding: 12px 14px;\n    background: var(--accent);\n    color: #fff;\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr));\n    gap: 12px;\n  }\n  .metric {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n  }\n  .metric-label {\n    font-size: 0.75rem;\n    opacity: 0.85;\n    margin-bottom: 2px;\n  }\n  .metric-value {\n    font-size: 1.1rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n  }\n  p.caption {\n    margin: 14px 0 0;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 480px) {\n    .metrics {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<h2>Adjust reproductive rate under fixed damage</h2>\n<p class=\"subhead\">Damage shortens individual lifespans. Faster reproduction keeps the population stable.</p>\n\n<div class=\"control\">\n  <label for=\"repro-rate\">Repro. rate:</label>\n  <input id=\"repro-rate\" type=\"range\" min=\"10\" max=\"50\" value=\"20\" aria-describedby=\"repro-out\">\n  <output id=\"repro-out\" for=\"repro-rate\">2.0×</output>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"timeline\">\n  <div class=\"timeline-title\">10-year window — generations over time</div>\n  <div class=\"gen-track\" id=\"gen-track\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"metrics\">\n  <div class=\"metric\">\n    <span class=\"metric-label\">Population size</span>\n    <span class=\"metric-value\" id=\"pop-size\">1000</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"metric\">\n    <span class=\"metric-label\">Avg. lifespan</span>\n    <span class=\"metric-value\" id=\"avg-life\">5.0 years</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"metric\">\n    <span class=\"metric-label\">Generations</span>\n    <span class=\"metric-value\" id=\"gen-count\">2</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"caption\" id=\"caption\">Slow reproduction produces too few generations to replace losses. Population shrinks.</p>\n\n<script>\n  (function () {\n    var slider = document.getElementById('repro-rate');\n    var reproOut = document.getElementById('repro-out');\n    var genTrack = document.getElementById('gen-track');\n    var popSize = document.getElementById('pop-size');\n    var avgLife = document.getElementById('avg-life');\n    var genCount = document.getElementById('gen-count');\n    var caption = document.getElementById('caption');\n\n    var BASELINE_LIFESPAN = 10;\n    var DAMAGE_FACTOR = 0.5;\n    var TIME_WINDOW = 10;\n    var TARGET_POP = 1000;\n\n    function update() {\n      var reproRate = +slider.value / 10;\n      reproOut.textContent = reproRate.toFixed(1) + '×';\n\n      var damagedLifespan = BASELINE_LIFESPAN * DAMAGE_FACTOR;\n      var genTime = damagedLifespan / reproRate;\n      var numGens = Math.floor(TIME_WINDOW / genTime);\n      \n      var replacementRate = reproRate;\n      var netGrowth = (replacementRate - 1.0) * numGens;\n      var finalPop = Math.max(0, Math.round(TARGET_POP * (1 + netGrowth * 0.15)));\n\n      popSize.textContent = finalPop;\n      avgLife.textContent = damagedLifespan.toFixed(1) + ' years';\n      genCount.textContent = numGens;\n\n      genTrack.innerHTML = '';\n      var markerWidth = Math.max(20, 100 / numGens);\n      for (var i = 0; i < numGens; i++) {\n        var marker = document.createElement('div');\n        marker.className = 'gen-marker';\n        marker.style.width = markerWidth + 'px';\n        if (i < numGens - 1) {\n          marker.classList.add('damaged');\n        }\n        genTrack.appendChild(marker);\n      }\n\n      if (reproRate < 2.0) {\n        caption.textContent = 'Slow reproduction produces too few generations to replace losses. Population shrinks.';\n      } else if (reproRate < 3.5) {\n        caption.textContent = 'Moderate acceleration matches losses. Generations cycle fast enough to hold population steady despite shortened lifespans.';\n      } else {\n        caption.textContent = 'High reproductive rate produces rapid generational turnover. Population size grows even as individual lifespans remain short.';\n      }\n    }\n\n    slider.addEventListener('input', update);\n    update();\n  })();\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>"
  }
}
